com.vector.annotations.publishedapi

Annotation Type PublishedMethod


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value={METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR})
 @PublishedApi(value=CLASS_DEPENDENCY)
public @interface PublishedMethod
    Indicates that the annotated method is part of an published type (see PublishedApi for more details), which must not be changed in the development without an approval for the breaking change!
